Excellent.

576
00:31:24,458 --> 00:31:26,166
Ready?

577
00:31:26,208 --> 00:31:27,792
Make it so.

578
00:31:36,333 --> 00:31:37,583
What the devil...?

579
00:31:37,625 --> 00:31:39,000
I was just playing.

580
00:31:39,041 --> 00:31:40,917
I'm sorry,
Captain.

581
00:31:59,709 --> 00:32:02,000
Alexander,
would you mind

