I'm afraid I can only
think of one way.

604
00:35:14,917 --> 00:35:16,041
What do you want?

605
00:35:16,083 --> 00:35:17,834
I need to see
my father.

606
00:35:17,875 --> 00:35:18,959
Go back inside.

607
00:35:19,000 --> 00:35:20,875
I need to see him
right now.

608
00:35:20,917 --> 00:35:22,709
Do not argue
with me.

609
00:35:22,750 --> 00:35:23,834
Go back inside.

610
00:35:23,875 --> 00:35:25,208
I need to see him now!

611
00:35:25,250 --> 00:35:28,458
Now! Now! Now! Now!
Now! Now! Now! Now!

612
00:35:28,500 --> 00:35:29,709
Stop it!
You hurt me!

613
00:35:29,750 --> 00:35:32,083
I want my father!
I want my father!

614
00:35:32,125 --> 00:35:34,417
All right.
Just stop that.

615
00:35:36,166 --> 00:35:38,083
