Let me go!

616
00:35:38,125 --> 00:35:40,500
Here he is.

617
00:35:40,542 --> 00:35:42,417
Now be quiet.

618
00:35:42,458 --> 00:35:43,709
What is going on?

619
00:35:43,750 --> 00:35:45,375
Dad!

620
00:35:53,792 --> 00:35:56,417
So, son,
how are you?

621
00:35:56,458 --> 00:35:57,834
I'm okay.

622
00:35:57,875 --> 00:36:00,750
And how are your friends--
Keiko and Guinan and Ro?

623
00:36:00,792 --> 00:36:03,166
They're okay, too.

624
00:36:03,208 --> 00:36:04,917
But...

625
00:36:04,959 --> 00:36:06,542
What's wrong?

626
00:36:06,583 --> 00:36:08,959
Well, we don't have
anything to do.

627
