None of the games
are working.

628
00:36:12,792 --> 00:36:17,291
I know, the Ferengi made Daddy
turn off the main computer.

629
00:36:17,333 --> 00:36:19,917
Well, can't you just
turn on the kid's computer

630
00:36:19,959 --> 00:36:21,792
