634
00:36:27,625 --> 00:36:29,834
Thanks, Number One.

635
00:36:33,583 --> 00:36:36,208
He's my number-one dad.

636
00:36:44,375 --> 00:36:45,625
CHILD 1:
Here they come.

637
00:36:45,667 --> 00:36:47,625
CHILD 2:
shh!

