Come in.

644
00:37:19,375 --> 00:37:22,834
I understand your son
was here to see you.

645
00:37:22,875 --> 00:37:25,208
That's right.

646
00:37:25,250 --> 00:37:27,792
We Ferengi do not
bring our offspring

647
00:37:27,834 --> 00:37:29,458
