aboard ship.

648
00:37:29,500 --> 00:37:31,542
Then I suppose
that's your loss.

649
00:37:31,583 --> 00:37:34,250
We consider our families
one of our strengths.

650
00:37:34,291 --> 00:37:38,375
I think you will find that
they can also be a weakness.

651
