00:39:21,417 --> 00:39:22,792
Don't touch that.

685
00:39:22,834 --> 00:39:24,625
You'll blow up the entire
firomactal drive.

686
00:39:24,667 --> 00:39:27,166
Oh, uh, wh-what...?
Wait... uh...

687
00:39:27,208 --> 00:39:30,625
what is a--
a firomactal drive?

688
00:39:31,625 --> 00:39:34,166
Well, just
explain it to me.

