00:43:48,458 --> 00:43:50,250
It's my turn,
isn't it?

743
00:43:50,291 --> 00:43:52,208
Only if you're ready.

744
00:43:54,375 --> 00:43:58,667
It's not quite as bad
as I remembered it.

745
00:43:58,709 --> 00:44:00,291
